Plan update
The verifier now implements the strict fee-on-transfer inventory-drain path with Balancer flash liquidity, whitelisted V2-router routing, dynamic fork-time candidate scanning, and progressive 2→6 round amplification. Validation was limited to local parsing/formatting because this environment cannot complete RPC-backed Foundry execution.
